              <p><strong>Position:</strong> President of Helby Studio SAS</p>
              <p><strong>Responsibility:</strong> Editorial responsibility for published content</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content-section">
          <h2>2. Contact details</h2>
          
