            <p><strong>Competent jurisdiction:</strong> Courts of Paris, France</p>
            <p><strong>Consumer disputes:</strong> European online dispute resolution platform available at <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr</a></p>
